ingerdients
================

* 1 c corn syruo
* 1 c sugar
* 1 c peanut butter
* 6 c rice krispies
* 6 oz chocolate chips
* 6 oz butterscotch chips

steps
=================
* bring corn syrup and sugar to boil
* fold mixture into rice krispies and peanut butter
* melt all chips in double boiler
* press rice krispie mixture into 9 x 13 pan
* spread melted chip mixture evenly over rice krispie mixture
* let cool at room temperature, or refridgerate